Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:57.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(180,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}无法拭去的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我们要用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的改进型?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：权天使高达，Throne系列的改进型）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam兄弟间的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够打啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗 阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不过托你们的福 半身都成焦炭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是那小子的命还不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混账
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生治疗费由你买单 用你的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}00和Seravee似乎已进入战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被A-LAWS逮着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好让他们开着Gundam去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系待机的阿勒路亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 库尔吉斯的小鬼 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是洛克昂的仇人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为他报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼看不见还上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起成佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四对一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是形势不利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 提耶利亚 皇小姐发来了返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是洛克昂的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的仇人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…还活着 阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不难缠就没得玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷杰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 宴会都泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹怒提耶利亚·艾迪的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是处理得当 本可收服他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我还事先做了铺垫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想让他们对抗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人越是活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就越能得到舆论支持
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将行动正当化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手光是KATARON也太不够看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗专用的我就没有出场机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Drive系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载两个GN Drive的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天人独自开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和TRANS-AM系统一样 是伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的性能远不及Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gadessa：GNZ-003  改革者开发的机体  机师为里维夫·里维尔）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次战斗中里维夫·里维尔会证明这点的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要给我出场机会啊 利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他们似乎顺利脱逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和变革者的对立会加速变革
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我身体的事 你不问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 感谢你的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回部队后就要开始Gundam追击作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前 由于Gundam的袭击 失去了父母及其他亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也被有毒GN粒子所伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身患细胞障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是复仇吗 那么年轻就走上战场的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是适合美丽礼服的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这青年是天人成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机体 Mr.武士道?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 各机收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全GN Drive 开始与托勒密连接作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上宇宙?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的预测 12小时以内敌人就会布下包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且去拉格朗日3的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以进行Gundam维修和接收支援机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以开始大气层脱离程序吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到路易丝了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她问了我关于你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回答说你在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么哥哥的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam的机师是阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯 他杀了洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我详情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史米卢佐夫少尉 阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安返航
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从Gundam失踪的地点 以及经过时间 移动速度来推测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰正在这一带海底航行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我队以6架Trilobite包围此区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现即开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制空权如何确保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个MS小队就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们应该不会从海底出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此战术我略有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰曾突破了大气层 降落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么反过来应该也可行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的GN Drive中 有名为TRANS-AM的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高浓度粒子全面释放系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个应该可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议和静止卫星轨道上展开的部队进行联动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的作战指挥官 应该也提前看穿刚才的传统战术了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼 你胆敢愚弄长官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有许可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是One man Amry吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Mr.武士道不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证遵从上校的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥为了给家人报仇 才被那个叫萨谢斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起世界变革 更看重私怨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒像是哥哥的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人去世都是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就无法这般执着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使仇人就在眼前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是KPSA…夺去你家人的组织成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么自责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我是去替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是渎神之举
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争是献给真主的圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对蔑视传统 践踏真主圣地的异教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要代替真主实行制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时若我阻止了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂…不 尼尔·狄兰提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用成为Meister了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那时你阻止了 还是会有恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法改变局势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘泥于过去也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我们不是为过去 而是为未来而战的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循自己的正义而活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那样能到达真正的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与变革者敌对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有真正的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在从事新型机开发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉…不 现在是Mr.武士道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人擅自这么叫的 烦人至极
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 今天为何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜就任开发部主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 希望让那架试作阶段的机体 染上我的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这才是此行的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何要求?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快的速度与最强的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 要保证将天人绳之以法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我只为此而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你所在的部队应该正是作战时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对舰队战没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对作战进程如此胸有成竹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼在此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队全体出击 Trilobite各机抵达索敌区域内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 发现敌舰的同时开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与本次作战无关 请你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型机吗 A-LAWS到底有多大规模和预算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会如何应对呢 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有报告给皇·李·诺列嘉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在整理思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我那之后发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到的扭曲点是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}变革中总伴随着痛楚 你们不也是过来人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}废话少说 干就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们是为计划而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伊欧利亚老爹把Gundam托付给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你们成为了伊欧利亚计划的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认六台敌人水中用MA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人正以包围之势靠近托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始预测时间是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0024
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人算到我们在赤道附近? 有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到副手席上 会有点摇晃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 进入紧急上浮模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任中东局势返回宇宙 为摆脱A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击预测时间只剩不到4秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时候 坚持到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队反应 是大型鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios Cherudim Seravee TRANS-AM开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大幅度展开 托勒密紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去爆炸点上方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将托勒密转为飞行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰高速浮出海面 还在继续上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他们真打算突破大气层?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我预测的还快 把Trilobite的攻击作为初速度利用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算出敌舰升空轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出了舰船范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许逃 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等豪气万丈的战术 果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升空轨道计算完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里维尔上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升空角度只需改变3度
